
```plantuml
@startuml FrogIT_GameLoop
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
autonumber

participant "FrogApp"          as App
participant "Event Processor"  as Evt
participant "Frog Collection"  as Col
participant "Frog"             as Frog
participant "Animation State"  as Anim
participant "Sprite Manager"   as Spr
participant "Render Pipeline"  as Pipe
participant "SFML Graphics"    as SFML

App -> App : clock.restart()\nget deltaTime

== Event Phase ==
App -> Evt : pollEvents()
Evt -> SFML : pollEvent()
SFML --> Evt : event queue
note right of Evt : close / click events\nhandled here (see 6.3)

== Update Phase ==
App -> Pipe : updateAll(deltaTime)
loop for each Frog in Collection
  Pipe -> Frog : update(deltaTime)
  Frog -> Anim : step(deltaTime)
  Anim -> Anim : calculate hop arc\nposition
  Anim --> Frog : new position
  Frog -> Spr : setPosition()\nselectFrame()
end

== Render Phase ==
App -> SFML : window.clear()
loop for each Frog in Collection
  Pipe -> Spr : draw()
  Spr -> SFML : window.draw(sprite)
end
App -> SFML : window.display()

@enduml
```